=========================================
Welcome to the Appcelerator Titanium SDK
=========================================

Appcelerator Titanium is an open source toolkit for building 
rich desktop applications using standard web technologies like
HTML, Javascript and CSS. Applications built on Titanium can
run on Win32, Mac OSX and Linux based operating systems.

You should also check out the Appcelerator SDK. The Appcelerator SDK
is an open source platform for building rich Internet applications.
You can find out more information about Appcelerator at <http://appcelerator.org>.

If you need more assistance, please go to the Appcelerator Developer Community
at <http://community.appcelerator.org>.

To report a bug or make a feature request, please visit our Issue Tracking portal
at <http://jira.appcelerator.org>.

If you are interested in becoming a community developer and contributing to
Appcelerator, please contact us at <info@appcelerator.com>.

If you need support, training or consulting assistance with Appcelerator, please
contact <sales@appcelerator.com> or visit the Appcelerator website at 
<http://appcelerator.org>.  


We hope you enjoy using Titanium, we sure do!

-- The Appcelerator Team


